title.narrative: Second Rural Water Supply and Sanitation Sector Project - Additional Financing

description.narrative: The project was designed to expand access to improved rural water supply and sanitation (RWSS) and to improve the health of rural residents in six provinces around the Tonle Sap Lake in Cambodia
